Hard to pick just 10 pics to sum up what was one of the most memorable trips of my life. @norwegiancruiseline has done it again with their beautiful brand new #norwegianviva. We were lucky enough to jump aboard her 3rd sailing with a 9 day itinerary for the ages. Starting in #Rome, we hit up #Naples #Palermo & #Siricusa #Sicily, #Corfu #Greece, #Split & #Zadar #Croatia, #Ravenna #Koper #Slovenia & #Trieste outside #Venice. And the food, fun & entertainment on board was just as enticing as all the sights to see and eat at each port. It was a bucket list moment to see the areas where my great grandparents came from (Naples, Sicily) and to visit new countries I’d never been. #cruisenorwegian

Have you ever called into a radio station? Skeery Jones used to record himself as a youngster calling into radio stations, hoping one day that could be him on the other side of the mic. Skeery’s dream became a reality.

You might have heard him on the air as the executive producer and on-air personalities on Elvis Duran and The Morning Show. “We’ve always been the morning show that wants to connect with the listener and make a difference in their day,” says Jones.

Listen to Elvis Duran and the Morning Show on Z100.
